title: Google : global corporate demography 2014 - 2019 , by gender
summary: Overall Female, and Male are roughly constant,  throughout the Year
The order of lines according to average values of Share of employees, in descending order is: 1. Male, and lastly, 2. Female.
Female reported the lowest Share of employees about 30.8 in Year 2017
The greatest difference of Share of employees between Female and Male occurs at Year 2017 and the smallest difference occurs at 2019.
